text: Caroline Verbraecken-De Loose (born 26 November 1924) was a Belgian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Belgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
